              = image_tag 'bio.png'
          .span7#bio-text
            %p.indent2x#who-i-am-content
              I am a Software Developer enjoying life in New Albany, Ohio.
              I enjoy writing software, playing video games, and anything computer hardware related.
              Nothing drives me more than the desire to learn new technologies.

        %h3#what-i-do
