          Apps, Websites, Testing! I enjoy writing quality, test-driven software in Ruby on Rails.
          I also have experience test-driving C# in ASP.NET MVC using a variety of testing tools.
          I am a strong proponent of Git and all of my personal code, this blog included, can be found on
          %a{href:'http://www.github.com/chrismagnacca/'}GitHub

        %p.indent2x.what-i-do-content
          Custom built PCs are a hobby of mine as well.
          I have built a variety of machines ranging from servers, gaming rigs, and hackintosh systems.
          In need of a new machine but don't know where to start?
          I am always interested in getting quality hardware together at the best possible price.

